<p>The Government Chemist is responsible under certain Acts of Parliament for providing independent analytical measurement and expert opinion to help avoid or resolve the disputes over scientific data, which arise from time to time between local authorities and the businesses that they regulate.</p>

<p>For more information about the work of the Government Chemist contact:</p>
